│ 329   /// has IncrementNUSW iff:                                            │
│ 330   ///                                                                   │
│ 331   /// 0 <= Unsigned(a) + Signed(b) < 2^n                                │
│ 332   ///                                                                   │
│ 333   /// The IncrementNSSW flag has identical semantics with               │
│ SCEV::FlagNSW.                                                              │
│ 334   ///                                                                   │
